Your home is your haven, that’s why when choosing a general contractor or home renovator it’s important to choose a company that can build in a way that complements your lifestyle. With our team of professional designers and skilled trades workers and connections to material and product suppliers, we can manage your project from concept to completion.We are a full service general contracting and design team. Our network of skilled electricians, carpenters and plumbers are ready to transform your home.

Founded by Architectural Designer, affiliated with many trades in Brantford, DFDBA.
I started helping with my dad flipping homes at a young age, gravitating to design from the very start. Spent my studies in the Architectural  Technology program at Mohawk college majoring in structural design. Whilst completing my diploma I worked for Feely Construction Ltd. to pay my way through school. Learning fast and diligently I acquired a love for the field of work and an admiration for all my mentors. I then tried my luck with another young aspiring company that fell through. At the end of 2018 I successfully completed my diploma for Architectural Technology and official started my business. Currently completing some BCIN certificates and studying for my real estate license, as well as working towards virtual reality design.
